Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.37,JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}	動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.96,JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}	あんたの血は極上だ
